      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for a solid value. While the engine and transmission are functional, there are visible signs of wear including some scratches on the body and minor stains on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require some routine maintenance such as new tires or a brake pad replacement. Overall, it\u2019s a reliable car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
