      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in showroom condition\u2014I've babied it since day one! There isn't a scratch or a dent to be found, and the interior still has that fresh car smell. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
